OL,3,CMother joins calls for maternity
OL,4,Creview at hospital trust after baby's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FA mother from Southwater near Horsham
OL,8,Fis calling on the Government to launch
OL,9,Fan independent inquiry into maternity
OL,10,Fcare in Sussex.
OL,12,FChloe Vowels Lovett's daughter Esme
OL,13,Fwas delivered at Worthing Hospital in
OL,14,F2022 but her heart was not beating.
OL,16,FShe says she her concerns during
OL,17,Fpregnancy were ignored.
OL,19,FAn internal review has since found
OL,20,Fthere were missed chances by medical
OL,21,Fstaff.
