OL,7,FMs Vowels Lovett says her "horrendous
OL,8,Fstabbing pains" which began 33 weeks
OL,9,Finto her pregnancy had been dismissed
OL,10,Fby hospital staff as normal.
OL,12,FA post-mortem examination and internal
OL,13,Finvestigation at Worthing hospital
OL,14,Flater found the 29-year-old, who was
OL,15,Fdeemed a high-risk pregnancy, had
OL,16,Fplacenta abruption and another
OL,17,Fcondition of polyhydramnios.
