OL,7,FThe findings also said medics missed
OL,8,Fat least six opportunities to have
OL,9,Fintervened before Esme's death,
OL,10,Faccording to law firm CL Medilaw.
OL,12,FMs Vowels Lovett and her husband Toby
OL,13,FLovett are campaigning for an
OL,14,Findependent review to take place into
OL,15,FUniversity Hospitals Sussex NHS
OL,16,FFoundation Trust, which runs Worthing
OL,17,FHospital and Royal Sussex County
OL,18,FHospital among others.
