OL,7,FSince her death, Ms Vowels Lovett
OL,8,Fsaid: "As time went on, we began
OL,9,Frealising that it wasn't just us that
OL,10,Fthis has happened to, there's more and
OL,11,Fmore of us and there's actually a
OL,12,Fgroup of us who have now come together
OL,13,Fwho have all lost babies with this
OL,14,Fparticular trust.
OL,16,F"I think it just pushes forward the
OL,17,Ffact that something more needs to be
OL,18,Fdone, because with all of us and our
OL,19,Fcases, we're all promised afterwards
OL,20,Fthis will change and we'll make these
OL,21,Fimprovements.
