OL,7,F"But meeting these other families,
OL,8,Fit's kind of a timeline that proves
OL,9,Fthat these changes aren't happening.
OL,10,FSo I think pushing for a review,
OL,11,Fhopefully we'll force their hand."
OL,13,FShe added: "I know for myself and
OL,14,Fothers, it almost feels like a little
OL,15,Fbit of justice for us. And obviously
OL,16,Fto try and help prevent other families
OL,17,Fgoing through the same thing.
OL,19,F"To lose a child when you shouldn't
OL,20,Fhave lost a child is just unbearable."
