OL,7,FThe campaign comes as an all-
OL,8,Fparliamentary inquiry into birth
OL,9,Ftrauma was published this week which
OL,10,Fheard from 1,300 people who had
OL,11,Ftraumatic birth experiences and
OL,12,Fconcluded that women are often
OL,13,F"treated as an inconvenience".
OL,15,FTrust bosses have apologised to the
OL,16,Ffamily for Esme's death and have said
OL,17,Fthe investigation from the incident
OL,18,Fhas led to improvements in the service.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@]O]
