OL,7,FThe University Hospitals Sussex Trust
OL,8,Fchief of women and children's
OL,9,Fdivision, Dr Tim Taylor, said: "We
OL,10,Fhave met with Esme's family to express
OL,11,Four deepest condolences and sincere
OL,12,Fapologies for their devastating loss,
OL,13,Fand I would like to repeat that
OL,14,Fapology publicly today.
OL,16,F"Following this tragedy in 2022, we
OL,17,Fcarried out an extensive investigation
OL,18,Fto help answer the family's questions.
OL,26,@qD@`OUxD@AOU
