OL,7,F"This led to significant improvements
OL,8,Fbeing made to the service, which we
OL,9,Fhave implemented and since shared with
OL,10,Fthe family."
OL,12,FSince the investigation ended in
OL,13,FOctober 2022, the trust has offered
OL,14,Furgent appointments for parents with
OL,15,Fcomplex medical issues, and launched a
OL,16,Fcentralised telephone triage service
OL,17,Famong other improvements.
